content: The PR summary comment now doesn't display a link to the results if no change was detected (e.g. https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/95914#issuecomment-1094642321). Was this intended? I would include the link always.

No, I'm guessing that got messed up in some of the refactoring. It's missing the top line:
